#: applications/luci-app-openwisp/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/openwisp.js:23
msgid "The Key of this device in the OpenWISP server."
msgstr "ກະແຈຂອງອຸປະກອນນີ້ໃນເຊີບເວີ OpenWISP."

